display_long_description:
🌀 Blazing Speed. Zero Limits. All in VR.
Unleash your inner ace pilot in Sky Striker: Chengdu Reborn. Strap in, blast off, and feel the raw power of futuristic flight—fully reimagined for VR.


⚡ Full-Throttle Immersion
Slam through real-world Chengdu and pulse-pounding cyberpunk skylines at breakneck speed. Dodge towers, dive under sky bridges, and thread the impossible with eye and hand control.


🎯 No Buttons. Just You and the Jet.
Harness the power of intuitive gaze and gesture flight. Tilt, roll, and react on instinct. It’s flight that feels natural—no joysticks, no distractions.


🌃 Landmarks Become Your Playground
Fly past the Chengdu Global Center, the Twin Towers, and more, all rebuilt in stunning VR. Each building becomes a part of your personal stunt course.


🧠 Secrets in the Skies
Find narrative fragments and hidden paths scattered through the city. Exploration rewards curiosity—can you piece together the truth behind the neon?


🚀 This is not just a race. It’s a takeover.
Own the skies. Push past limits. Welcome to the next generation of VR flight.
